Personally of all the ideas floating about the ones I love the most...<br>
<br>
1. Make seperate ac tables based on armor type. ie 1300ac monk != 1300ac war<br>
<br>
2. Give wars a natural damage mitigation.<br>
<br>
3. Defensive/Offensive Slider. You can slide from fully defensive to fully offensive. No timer.<br>
<br>
4. Item stats based on class. Items should reflect the class using it. Ie a BP for a plate class could be...<br>
War:- 150hp 20sta 20 str   15dex 15agi 10 all saves<br>
Pal :-  100hp 50mana 15stam 15 str 10wis 15dex/agi 10svs<br>
SK :- 100hp 50mana 15stam 15str 10int 15dex/agi 10svs<br>
Cleric:- 50hp 100mana 15stam 15 str 10wix 15dex/agi 10svs<br>
<br>
5. Fix taunt already.<br>
<br>
Just some ideas I saw and liked most.<br>
